data.description: YOUR SEARCH IS OVER!!!    Welcome to Country Club Estates off of Belingrath Rd!   This charming house is waiting for its new owners with 3 beds and 2 full bath. Approximately 1500sqft living area. Large fenced backyard, carport and plenty of parking.The home features nice sized bedrooms and an open living room.  Refrigerator and security system remain at property.   UPDATES PER SELLER:  ROOF AND AC 2023  HVAC 2022  White bathroom counter top not installed but will remain in the house for its new owner     USDA AREA... 0% DOWN PAYMENT for qualified buyers.  NO HOA...    Call your favorite realtor today and schedule a showing!!
